{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":624,"text":"It is said that the grass is always greener"},{"time":4672,"text":"on the other side of the fence,"},{"time":7726,"text":"and I believe this is true,"},{"time":10872,"text":"especially when I hear President Obama"},{"time":13456,"text":"often talk about the Korean education system"},{"time":15954,"text":"as a benchmark of success."},{"time":19465,"text":"Well, I can tell you that,"},{"time":21862,"text":"in the rigid structure and highly competitive nature"},{"time":25409,"text":"of the Korean school system,"},{"time":27600,"text":"also known as pressure cooker,"},{"time":29934,"text":"not everyone can do well in that environment."},{"time":35593,"text":"While many people responded in different ways"},{"time":38218,"text":"about our education system,"},{"time":41218,"text":"my response to the high-pressure environment"},{"time":44594,"text":"was making bows with pieces of wood"},{"time":47524,"text":"found near my apartment building."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50268,"text":"Why bows?"},{"time":52788,"text":"I'm not quite sure."},{"time":55539,"text":"Perhaps, in the face of constant pressure,"},{"time":59484,"text":"my caveman instinct of survival"},{"time":61731,"text":"has connected with the bows."},{"time":66053,"text":"If you think about it,"},{"time":67787,"text":"the bow has really helped drive human survival"},{"time":71200,"text":"since prehistoric times."},{"time":73925,"text":"The area within three kilometers of my home"},{"time":77192,"text":"used to be a mulberry forest"},{"time":79375,"text":"during the Joseon dynasty,"},{"time":81665,"text":"where silkworms were fed with mulberry leaves."},{"time":86122,"text":"In order to raise the historical awareness of this fact,"},{"time":90828,"text":"the government has planted mulberry trees."},{"time":95163,"text":"The seeds from these trees"},{"time":96941,"text":"also have spread by birds here and there"},{"time":99740,"text":"nearby the soundproof walls of the city expressway"},{"time":103218,"text":"that has been built around the 1988 Olympics."},{"time":107584,"text":"The area near these walls,"},{"time":110085,"text":"which nobody bothers to pay attention to,"},{"time":113065,"text":"had been left free from major intervention,"},{"time":116259,"text":"and this is where I first found my treasures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122159,"text":"As I fell deeper into bow making,"},{"time":125360,"text":"I began to search far and beyond my neighborhood."},{"time":129571,"text":"When I went on school field trips,"},{"time":131689,"text":"family vacations, or simply on my way home"},{"time":134928,"text":"from extracurricular classes,"},{"time":137763,"text":"I wandered around wooded areas"},{"time":139862,"text":"and gathered tree branches"},{"time":141601,"text":"with the tools that I sneaked inside my school bag."},{"time":145572,"text":"And they would be somethings like saws, knives,"},{"time":149273,"text":"sickles and axes"},{"time":151519,"text":"that I covered up with a piece of towel."},{"time":156207,"text":"I would bring the branches home,"},{"time":158088,"text":"riding buses and subways,"},{"time":160077,"text":"barely holding them in my hands."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163466,"text":"And I did not bring the tools here to Long Beach."},{"time":167342,"text":"Airport security."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168898,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":170978,"text":"In the privacy of my room, covered in sawdust,"},{"time":174697,"text":"I would saw, trim and polish wood all night long"},{"time":178751,"text":"until a bow took shape."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181218,"text":"One day, I was changing the shape of a bamboo piece"},{"time":185713,"text":"and ended up setting the place on fire."},{"time":190468,"text":"Where? The rooftop of my apartment building,"},{"time":195257,"text":"a place where 96 families call home."},{"time":198897,"text":"A customer from a department store across from my building"},{"time":201488,"text":"called 911,"},{"time":202978,"text":"and I ran downstairs to tell my mom"},{"time":205025,"text":"with half of my hair burned."},{"time":210242,"text":"I want to take this opportunity"},{"time":212370,"text":"to tell my mom, in the audience today:"},{"time":216074,"text":"Mom, I was really sorry,"},{"time":218415,"text":"and I will be more careful with open fire from now on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222061,"text":"My mother had to do a lot of explaining,"},{"time":224695,"text":"telling people that her son did not commit"},{"time":227024,"text":"a premeditated arson."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233250,"text":"I also researched extensively on bows around the world."},{"time":237420,"text":"In that process, I tried to combine"},{"time":239466,"text":"the different bows from across time and places"},{"time":241907,"text":"to create the most effective bow."},{"time":245690,"text":"I also worked with many different types of wood,"},{"time":248043,"text":"such as maple, yew and mulberry,"},{"time":251231,"text":"and did many shooting experiments"},{"time":253171,"text":"in the wooded area near the urban expressway"},{"time":255670,"text":"that I mentioned before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258505,"text":"The most effective bow for me"},{"time":260530,"text":"would be like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263297,"text":"One: Curved tips can maximize the springiness"},{"time":267510,"text":"when you draw and shoot the arrow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271041,"text":"Two: Belly is drawn inward for higher draw weight,"},{"time":275938,"text":"which means more power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279599,"text":"Three: Sinew used in the outer layer of the limb"},{"time":283911,"text":"for maximum tension storage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286816,"text":"And four: Horn used to store energy in compression."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295055,"text":"After fixing, breaking, redesigning,"},{"time":298053,"text":"mending, bending and amending,"},{"time":300984,"text":"my ideal bow began to take shape,"},{"time":304291,"text":"and when it was finally done,"},{"time":308146,"text":"it looked like this."},{"time":312673,"text":"I was so proud of myself"},{"time":314910,"text":"for inventing a perfect bow on my own."},{"time":320984,"text":"This is a picture of Korean traditional bows"},{"time":324416,"text":"taken from a museum,"},{"time":326312,"text":"and see how my bow resembles them."},{"time":331796,"text":"Thanks to my ancestors"},{"time":333362,"text":"for robbing me of my invention. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":339542,"text":"Through bowmaking,"},{"time":341394,"text":"I came in contact with part of my heritage."},{"time":344455,"text":"Learning the information that has accumulated over time"},{"time":348018,"text":"and reading the message left by my ancestors"},{"time":350856,"text":"were better than any consolation therapy"},{"time":353455,"text":"or piece of advice any living adults could give me."},{"time":358404,"text":"You see, I searched far and wide,"},{"time":361322,"text":"but never bothered to look close and near."},{"time":364798,"text":"From this realization,"},{"time":367043,"text":"I began to take interest in Korean history,"},{"time":369864,"text":"which had never inspired me before."},{"time":373261,"text":"In the end, the grass is often greener"},{"time":376637,"text":"on my side of the fence,"},{"time":378427,"text":"although we don't realize it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381604,"text":"Now, I am going to show you how my bow works."},{"time":386355,"text":"And let's see how this one works."},{"time":391568,"text":"This is a bamboo bow,"},{"time":393705,"text":"with 45-pound draw weights."},{"time":397637,"text":"(Noise of shooting arrow)"},{"time":399821,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":408285,"text":"A bow may function in a simple mechanism,"},{"time":412694,"text":"but in order to make a good bow,"},{"time":415245,"text":"a great amount of sensitivity is required."},{"time":419257,"text":"You need to console and communicate"},{"time":421787,"text":"with the wood material."},{"time":424533,"text":"Each fiber in the wood"},{"time":426225,"text":"has its own reason and function for being,"},{"time":429051,"text":"and only through cooperation and harmony among them"},{"time":432446,"text":"comes a great bow."},{"time":436043,"text":"I may be an [odd] student"},{"time":437833,"text":"with unconventional interests,"},{"time":440024,"text":"but I hope I am making a contribution"},{"time":442966,"text":"by sharing my story with all of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446855,"text":"My ideal world is a place"},{"time":449108,"text":"where no one is left behind,"},{"time":451321,"text":"where everyone is needed exactly where they are,"},{"time":454614,"text":"like the fibers and the tendons in a bow,"},{"time":458210,"text":"a place where the strong is flexible"},{"time":461479,"text":"and the vulnerable is resilient."},{"time":465272,"text":"The bow resembles me,"},{"time":466923,"text":"and I resemble the bow."},{"time":469971,"text":"Now, I am shooting a part of myself to you."},{"time":474835,"text":"No, better yet, a part of my mind"},{"time":477585,"text":"has just been shot over to your mind."},{"time":480424,"text":"Did it strike you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":482668,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484208,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}